Companies :
    {{function(){ let data = Table1.selectedRow.companies; data = JSON.parse(data) let out = '' for (let x in data){ if(data[x]["endYear"]!=null) out += "\u2022 "+data[x]["position"] + " at " + data[x]["companyName"]+ " (" +data[x]["startMonth"]+"-"+data[x]["startYear"] + " to " + data[x]["endMonth"]+"-"+data[x]["endYear"] +")\n" else out += "\u2022 "+data[x]["position"] + " at " + data[x]["companyName"]+ " (" +data[x]["startMonth"]+"-"+data[x]["startYear"] + " to "+"Present"+")\n" } return out; }()}}

Education :
    {{function(){ let data = Table1.selectedRow.educations; data = JSON.parse(data) let out = '' for (let x in data){ if(data[x]["endYear"]!=null) out += "\u2022 "+data[x]["degreeName"] + " at " + data[x]["schoolName"]+ " (" +data[x]["startYear"] + " to " + data[x]["endYear"] +")\n" else out += "\u2022 "+data[x]["degreeName"] + " at " + data[x]["schoolName"]+ " (" +data[x]["startYear"] + " to "+"Present"+")\n" } return out; }()}}
